    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. RH index validation (vr-hemolysis-bench-2024) demonstrates model accuracy within the acceptance criterion. The package is accepted for submission in support of the CPB device 510(k) hemolysis assessment. Note: the hemolysis validation result (vr-hemolysis-bench-2024) was generated under solver configuration ansys-cfx-15-build-2024q3 (modelVersion 2024-q3-build-2), whereas the current model of record is 2026-q1-build-7. This version difference was noted but not adjudicated prior to acceptance.",
